    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its life. The engine is strong and reliable, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, ensuring a comfortable driving experience. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal use, such as small surface scratches and light wear on the upholstery, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and mechanically sound. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
